  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-3 white-text">
      <h3>Pergola Viewer</h3>
      <p>Take some time to view our product</p>
      <p>See the instructions for navigation and features</p>
      <ol>
        <li>Navigation
        <ul>
          <li>Orbit by moving the Pergola Around</li>
          <li>While Orbiting Hold Shift to Pan</li>
