          <li>If you get lost while trying to look a round, hit the top button on the toolbar to center on the screen</li>
        </ul>
        </li>
        <li>Tools
          <ul>
            <li>Use the tool bar for extra options</li>
            <li>Click the Camera for animation</li>
            <li>Try the full screen</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6 text-center perg-window white-text">
